{"tid":619734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大橋管理局回應崩堤　 認弱波石會移位　 稱設計容許　工程師轟死不認錯","createTime":"2018-04-07T02:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T03:44:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ab683c5754f8ddc2eddf0c7c4a78f80e5c665afb","tid":619734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"大橋管理局回應崩堤　<br />\n認弱波石會移位　<br />\n稱設計容許　工程師轟死不認錯<br />\n<br />\n27,087<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180407/large/07la4p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180407%2Flarge%2F07la4p2.jpg&h=f62684d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港珠澳大橋人工島於今年4月有大量弱波石漂散海面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港珠澳大橋東西人工島被質疑防波堤崩塌。大橋管理局昨首次承認，從工程角度而言，弱波石設計已預計受潮浪拍打下有「容許的移位」，如發現弱波石局部空缺或堆積，將及時安排檢查及維修。工程師黎廣德指，當局變相承認隨機放置弱波石的缺點，包括可被波浪衝擊移位、惡劣天氣下要密切監察等。路政署明日赴珠海與大橋管理局會面商討事件。<br />\n<br />\n記者：潘柏林<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大橋管理局繼周三後，昨晚第二度解釋人工島防波堤設計，強調根據工程情況，特意設計在水面下隨機安放弱波石，亦曾進行物理模型試驗，驗證有關方案更可靠有效。管理局又貼上相片，指防護效果經受颱風「天鴿」的實際驗證。局方引述人工島諮詢技術總負責人Dick Kevelam指，香港媒體誤讀了航拍圖片，以為是人工島防波堤崩塌或被衝散，實際是人為特意這樣安放。<br />\n<br />\n本港工程界質疑隨機放置無法抵擋海浪沖擊，導致弱波石移位。管理局承認，從工程角度來看，弱波石的設計已經預計了受潮浪拍打情況下容許的位移；當局除日常定期巡查外，在經歷惡劣天氣及海況後會進行專項巡測，如發現弱波石局部空缺或堆積，將及時安排檢查及進行維修，確保結構安全及完整。目前未發現局部空缺或堆積等異常現象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路政署明赴珠海商討<br />\n<br />\n土木及結構工程師蘇耀坤指，正常互相扣連的弱波石，在浪潮打擊下只會越收越緊。但航拍照片可見部份弱波石沒有扣連，質疑大橋管理局「容許移位」標準為何，「就唔係好似𠵱家咁，一嚿走咗去100米以外，跟住話可容許移位，有乜可能呢？」他批評當局不願面對問題，「你死撐唔肯認錯，呢啲結構一定係會受天氣考驗」。<br />\n<br />\n工程師黎廣德指，管理局的說法變相承認隨機擺放的缺點，弱波石移位幅度一大，便削弱防坡堤的功能，「要不停監測、不停補救，佢都話咯，惡劣天氣後要專項加查」。他促請大橋管理局公佈弱波石分佈圖，對照現時弱波石有否移位。<br />\n<br />\n路政署指，明日將前往珠海與大橋管理局會面商討有關事宜，有需要的話不排除到人工島跟進。署方承認高級工程師李競偉擔任大橋管理局副局長一職，但無回應他有否向港府匯報弱波石情況。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥昨稱，不希望外界憑一張相片就懷疑工程設計有問題，如公眾認為管理局的解釋太深奧，政府可以再協助跟進。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆指，非常關注大橋的安全，但需要給予時間讓大橋管理局解說。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n涉掟銀狐犬落樓分屍　被告不准保釋<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n內地文獻稱　可擋三百年一遇波浪<br />\n<br />\n內地文獻稱　可擋三百年一遇波浪"},{"pid":"7bf5f27a8420acf5a7e34fe73e6107b71dd8a693","tid":619734,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"越描越黑"},{"pid":"47a1e11c96cd3f6ffc0ab364232f3282838d5879","tid":619734,"uid":37739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"支那人死不認錯, 堅持中國特色防波提 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81902aea42208e48b8517c571b4ca04c70a10e6","tid":619734,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:03:30.000Z","msg":"唔係隨機咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327e266441e4c63a424cdaaba4ae733ff22345c3","tid":619734,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"林鄭識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前幾日仲話唔好單憑張相相信"},{"pid":"66eedf83d70428dad6c6604a95b6129be3b0cee9","tid":619734,"uid":104443,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「下一則<br />\n內地文獻稱　可擋三百年一遇波浪<br />\n<br />\n內地文獻稱　可擋三百年一遇波浪」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/111811_dc4a276fa6111a688c54f0ff4e607276.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F111811_dc4a276fa6111a688c54f0ff4e607276.png&h=0c3a7822&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f89f6e589dd5107089f368a0e5a6ccb8f0928092","tid":619734,"uid":88886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"時間証明一切<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下到時點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c952953d9ecf450342b15f757d1e7196555219","tid":619734,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/113125_74692c120bb7a45498c6a496432247ee.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F113125_74692c120bb7a45498c6a496432247ee.gif&h=84615fea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4dbdc0cae36cfe8733b98f31c596e2abf754a88","tid":619734,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:33:10.000Z","msg":"隨機放， 隨機飄移， 這才是破海浪既最佳方法。<br />\n<br />\n海浪無聲無形的撲來， 我(防波石) 順水推舟的卸去， 化波浪於無形。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結合太極精綷， 超英趕美超荷創世之作。"},{"pid":"9d4d1cf9aebae0453599370686943c1a28cab71f","tid":619734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"水無處不入 無堅不摧， 唯隨機飄移可破。"},{"pid":"33f871ff04a2cbc0216ca07594b31a74c57a5958","tid":619734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180407/20354361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F20354361&d=S3axBjbT7DzXQv2YFLyEHdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f48afce3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F20354361&h=915d7b9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180407/20354361</a>"},{"pid":"d0e533db4abc9e51a15f913e946be11b4879d2f9","tid":619734,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"有無專業人士講下係咪堅"},{"pid":"da9d00d17d20770b920ebc67d2e48530aa292fa0","tid":619734,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"內地文獻稱　可擋三百年一遇波浪<br />\n<br />\n啱啊<br />\n擋完咪沉入大海囉 <br />\n所以其實可以吹到「可擋萬年一遇」都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}